(0, 'The wind and waves are always on the side of the ablest\r\nnavigators.\r\n\r\n	-- Edward Gibbon'),
(0, 'Be prepared to accept sacrifices.  Vestal virgins aren''t all that bad.'),
(0, 'Proverbs 28:18\nHe whose walk is blameless is kept safe, but he whose ways are \nperverse will suddenly fall.'),
