(0, 'After all, what is your hosts'' purpose in having a party?\r\nSurely not for you to enjoy yourself; if that were their sole\r\npurpose, they''d have simply sent champagne and women over to\r\nyour place by taxi.\r\n\r\n	-- P. J. O''Rourke'),
(0, '... though his invention worked superbly -- his theory was a crock of sewage\nfrom beginning to end.\n		-- Vernor Vinge, "The Peace War"'),
